\title{The monitorability prism}
\author{liamoc}
\date{2026-06-21}
\p{[[kaiphan]] has been building on her already [very impressive result](loc-0046) to produce a very nice picture of the monitorability landscape. I will present a brief summary of her results here, but eventually they will be incorporated into my [research notebook](ltp-0001) on linear-time temporal properties. Mostly, our results concern the space of program [properties](ltp-0003) — sets of program [behaviours](ltp-0002).}
\figure{
  \tex{\usepackage{tikz-cd}}{
    \begin{tikzcd}
    	& {\mathsf{Decision}} & \\
    	& {\textsf{Quasi-decision}} \\
